{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":880,"text":"June 2010."},{"time":3760,"text":"I landed for the first time\nin Rome, Italy."},{"time":7800,"text":"I wasn't there to sightsee."},{"time":9720,"text":"I was there to solve world hunger."}]},{"cues":[{"time":13160,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":15280,"text":"That's right."},{"time":16520,"text":"I was a 25-year-old PhD student"},{"time":18640,"text":"armed with a prototype tool\ndeveloped back at my university,"},{"time":21760,"text":"and I was going to help\nthe World Food Programme fix hunger."},{"time":25840,"text":"So I strode into the headquarters building"},{"time":28600,"text":"and my eyes scanned the row of UN flags,"},{"time":31440,"text":"and I smiled as I thought to myself,"},{"time":34840,"text":"\"The engineer is here.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":36480,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":38720,"text":"Give me your data."},{"time":40520,"text":"I'm going to optimize everything."}]},{"cues":[{"time":42720,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":44480,"text":"Tell me the food that you've purchased,"},{"time":46400,"text":"tell me where it's going\nand when it needs to be there,"},{"time":49040,"text":"and I'm going to tell you\nthe shortest, fastest, cheapest,"},{"time":51800,"text":"best set of routes to take for the food."},{"time":53760,"text":"We're going to save money,"},{"time":55280,"text":"we're going to avoid\ndelays and disruptions,"},{"time":57400,"text":"and bottom line,\nwe're going to save lives."},{"time":60160,"text":"You're welcome."}]},{"cues":[{"time":61400,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":63120,"text":"I thought it was going to take 12 months,"},{"time":65120,"text":"OK, maybe even 13."},{"time":67800,"text":"This is not quite how it panned out."},{"time":71600,"text":"Just a couple of months into the project,\nmy French boss, he told me,"},{"time":75400,"text":"\"You know, Mallory,"},{"time":77240,"text":"it's a good idea,"},{"time":78920,"text":"but the data you need\nfor your algorithms is not there."},{"time":82280,"text":"It's the right idea but at the wrong time,"},{"time":84840,"text":"and the right idea at the wrong time"},{"time":87160,"text":"is the wrong idea.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":88560,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":90960,"text":"Project over."},{"time":93120,"text":"I was crushed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":97000,"text":"When I look back now"},{"time":98480,"text":"on that first summer in Rome"},{"time":100160,"text":"and I see how much has changed\nover the past six years,"},{"time":102840,"text":"it is an absolute transformation."},{"time":105640,"text":"It's a coming of age for bringing data\ninto the humanitarian world."},{"time":110160,"text":"It's exciting. It's inspiring."},{"time":112840,"text":"But we're not there yet."},{"time":115320,"text":"And brace yourself, executives,"},{"time":117640,"text":"because I'm going to be putting companies"},{"time":119640,"text":"on the hot seat to step up\nand play the role that I know they can."}]},{"cues":[{"time":125520,"text":"My experiences back in Rome prove"},{"time":128360,"text":"using data you can save lives."},{"time":131440,"text":"OK, not that first attempt,"},{"time":133920,"text":"but eventually we got there."},{"time":136520,"text":"Let me paint the picture for you."},{"time":138280,"text":"Imagine that you have to plan\nbreakfast, lunch and dinner"},{"time":141040,"text":"for 500,000 people,"},{"time":142680,"text":"and you only have\na certain budget to do it,"},{"time":144840,"text":"say 6.5 million dollars per month."},{"time":148920,"text":"Well, what should you do?\nWhat's the best way to handle it?"},{"time":152280,"text":"Should you buy rice, wheat, chickpea, oil?"},{"time":155760,"text":"How much?"},{"time":157000,"text":"It sounds simple. It's not."},{"time":159160,"text":"You have 30 possible foods,\nand you have to pick five of them."},{"time":162400,"text":"That's already over 140,000\ndifferent combinations."},{"time":165840,"text":"Then for each food that you pick,"},{"time":167560,"text":"you need to decide how much you'll buy,"},{"time":169560,"text":"where you're going to get it from,"},{"time":171280,"text":"where you're going to store it,"},{"time":173760,"text":"how long it's going to take to get there."},{"time":175760,"text":"You need to look at all of the different\ntransportation routes as well."},{"time":179120,"text":"And that's already\nover 900 million options."},{"time":182120,"text":"If you considered each option\nfor a single second,"},{"time":184520,"text":"that would take you\nover 28 years to get through."},{"time":186880,"text":"900 million options."}]},{"cues":[{"time":189160,"text":"So we created a tool\nthat allowed decisionmakers"},{"time":191640,"text":"to weed through all 900 million options"},{"time":194280,"text":"in just a matter of days."},{"time":196560,"text":"It turned out to be incredibly successful."},{"time":199400,"text":"In an operation in Iraq,"},{"time":200680,"text":"we saved 17 percent of the costs,"},{"time":203240,"text":"and this meant that you had the ability\nto feed an additional 80,000 people."},{"time":207400,"text":"It's all thanks to the use of data\nand modeling complex systems."}]},{"cues":[{"time":212800,"text":"But we didn't do it alone."},{"time":214840,"text":"The unit that I worked with in Rome,\nthey were unique."},{"time":217600,"text":"They believed in collaboration."},{"time":219360,"text":"They brought in the academic world."},{"time":221080,"text":"They brought in companies."},{"time":223200,"text":"And if we really want to make big changes\nin big problems like world hunger,"},{"time":226840,"text":"we need everybody to the table."},{"time":230040,"text":"We need the data people\nfrom humanitarian organizations"},{"time":233000,"text":"leading the way,"},{"time":234280,"text":"and orchestrating\njust the right types of engagements"},{"time":236880,"text":"with academics, with governments."},{"time":238600,"text":"And there's one group that's not being\nleveraged in the way that it should be."},{"time":242320,"text":"Did you guess it? Companies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":244440,"text":"Companies have a major role to play\nin fixing the big problems in our world."},{"time":248880,"text":"I've been in the private sector\nfor two years now."},{"time":251320,"text":"I've seen what companies can do,\nand I've seen what companies aren't doing,"},{"time":254920,"text":"and I think there's three main ways\nthat we can fill that gap:"},{"time":258320,"text":"by donating data,\nby donating decision scientists"},{"time":261440,"text":"and by donating technology\nto gather new sources of data."},{"time":265920,"text":"This is data philanthropy,"},{"time":267520,"text":"and it's the future of corporate\nsocial responsibility."},{"time":271160,"text":"Bonus, it also makes good business sense."}]},{"cues":[{"time":274920,"text":"Companies today,\nthey collect mountains of data,"},{"time":278160,"text":"so the first thing they can do\nis start donating that data."},{"time":280946,"text":"Some companies are already doing it."},{"time":283160,"text":"Take, for example,\na major telecom company."},{"time":285600,"text":"They opened up their data\nin Senegal and the Ivory Coast"},{"time":288400,"text":"and researchers discovered"},{"time":290400,"text":"that if you look at the patterns\nin the pings to the cell phone towers,"},{"time":293758,"text":"you can see where people are traveling."},{"time":295720,"text":"And that can tell you things like"},{"time":297920,"text":"where malaria might spread,\nand you can make predictions with it."},{"time":301040,"text":"Or take for example\nan innovative satellite company."},{"time":303960,"text":"They opened up their data and donated it,"},{"time":306000,"text":"and with that data you could track"},{"time":307680,"text":"how droughts are impacting\nfood production."},{"time":310920,"text":"With that you can actually trigger\naid funding before a crisis can happen."}]},{"cues":[{"time":315560,"text":"This is a great start."},{"time":317840,"text":"There's important insights\njust locked away in company data."},{"time":322480,"text":"And yes, you need to be very careful."},{"time":324320,"text":"You need to respect privacy concerns,\nfor example by anonymizing the data."}]},{"cues":[{"time":327920,"text":"But even if the floodgates opened up,"},{"time":330720,"text":"and even if all companies\ndonated their data"},{"time":333280,"text":"to academics, to NGOs,\nto humanitarian organizations,"},{"time":336560,"text":"it wouldn't be enough\nto harness that full impact of data"},{"time":339560,"text":"for humanitarian goals."},{"time":342320,"text":"Why?"},{"time":343800,"text":"To unlock insights in data,\nyou need decision scientists."},{"time":347760,"text":"Decision scientists are people like me."},{"time":350360,"text":"They take the data, they clean it up,"},{"time":352200,"text":"transform it and put it\ninto a useful algorithm"},{"time":354480,"text":"that's the best choice\nto address the business need at hand."},{"time":357800,"text":"In the world of humanitarian aid,\nthere are very few decision scientists."},{"time":361520,"text":"Most of them work for companies."},{"time":364480,"text":"So that's the second thing\nthat companies need to do."},{"time":367000,"text":"In addition to donating their data,"},{"time":368720,"text":"they need to donate\ntheir decision scientists."}]},{"cues":[{"time":371520,"text":"Now, companies will say, \"Ah! Don't take\nour decision scientists from us."},{"time":377280,"text":"We need every spare second of their time.\""},{"time":380360,"text":"But there's a way."},{"time":383200,"text":"If a company was going to donate\na block of a decision scientist's time,"},{"time":386640,"text":"it would actually make more sense\nto spread out that block of time"},{"time":389800,"text":"over a long period,\nsay for example five years."},{"time":392600,"text":"This might only amount\nto a couple of hours per month,"},{"time":395680,"text":"which a company would hardly miss,"},{"time":397760,"text":"but what it enables is really important:\nlong-term partnerships."},{"time":402920,"text":"Long-term partnerships\nallow you to build relationships,"},{"time":405760,"text":"to get to know the data,\nto really understand it"},{"time":408440,"text":"and to start to understand\nthe needs and challenges"},{"time":410880,"text":"that the humanitarian\norganization is facing."},{"time":414345,"text":"In Rome, at the World Food Programme,\nthis took us five years to do,"},{"time":417560,"text":"five years."},{"time":419040,"text":"That first three years, OK,\nthat was just what we couldn't solve for."},{"time":422400,"text":"Then there was two years after that\nof refining and implementing the tool,"},{"time":425920,"text":"like in the operations in Iraq\nand other countries."},{"time":429520,"text":"I don't think that's\nan unrealistic timeline"},{"time":431640,"text":"when it comes to using data\nto make operational changes."},{"time":434400,"text":"It's an investment. It requires patience."},{"time":437760,"text":"But the types of results\nthat can be produced are undeniable."},{"time":441280,"text":"In our case, it was the ability\nto feed tens of thousands more people."}]},{"cues":[{"time":447440,"text":"So we have donating data,\nwe have donating decision scientists,"},{"time":451800,"text":"and there's actually a third way\nthat companies can help:"},{"time":454520,"text":"donating technology\nto capture new sources of data."},{"time":457520,"text":"You see, there's a lot of things\nwe just don't have data on."},{"time":460960,"text":"Right now, Syrian refugees\nare flooding into Greece,"},{"time":465120,"text":"and the UN refugee agency,\nthey have their hands full."},{"time":469000,"text":"The current system for tracking people\nis paper and pencil,"},{"time":472080,"text":"and what that means is"},{"time":473360,"text":"that when a mother and her five children\nwalk into the camp,"},{"time":476240,"text":"headquarters is essentially\nblind to this moment."},{"time":478920,"text":"That's all going to change\nin the next few weeks,"},{"time":481280,"text":"thanks to private sector collaboration."},{"time":483840,"text":"There's going to be a new system based\non donated package tracking technology"},{"time":487520,"text":"from the logistics company\nthat I work for."},{"time":490120,"text":"With this new system,\nthere will be a data trail,"},{"time":492480,"text":"so you know exactly the moment"},{"time":493960,"text":"when that mother and her children\nwalk into the camp."},{"time":496480,"text":"And even more, you know\nif she's going to have supplies"},{"time":499120,"text":"this month and the next."},{"time":500400,"text":"Information visibility drives efficiency."},{"time":503440,"text":"For companies, using technology\nto gather important data,"},{"time":506720,"text":"it's like bread and butter."},{"time":508200,"text":"They've been doing it for years,"},{"time":509800,"text":"and it's led to major\noperational efficiency improvements."},{"time":513080,"text":"Just try to imagine\nyour favorite beverage company"},{"time":516280,"text":"trying to plan their inventory"},{"time":517880,"text":"and not knowing how many bottles\nwere on the shelves."},{"time":520400,"text":"It's absurd."},{"time":521640,"text":"Data drives better decisions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":525800,"text":"Now, if you're representing a company,"},{"time":528360,"text":"and you're pragmatic\nand not just idealistic,"},{"time":531520,"text":"you might be saying to yourself,\n\"OK, this is all great, Mallory,"},{"time":534600,"text":"but why should I want to be involved?\""},{"time":537000,"text":"Well for one thing, beyond the good PR,"},{"time":539840,"text":"humanitarian aid\nis a 24-billion-dollar sector,"},{"time":542640,"text":"and there's over five billion people,\nmaybe your next customers,"},{"time":545720,"text":"that live in the developing world."},{"time":547560,"text":"Further, companies that are engaging\nin data philanthropy,"},{"time":550680,"text":"they're finding new insights\nlocked away in their data."},{"time":553680,"text":"Take, for example, a credit card company"},{"time":555960,"text":"that's opened up a center"},{"time":557320,"text":"that functions as a hub for academics,\nfor NGOs and governments,"},{"time":560720,"text":"all working together."},{"time":563040,"text":"They're looking at information\nin credit card swipes"},{"time":565800,"text":"and using that to find insights\nabout how households in India"},{"time":568800,"text":"live, work, earn and spend."},{"time":571680,"text":"For the humanitarian world,\nthis provides information"},{"time":574280,"text":"about how you might\nbring people out of poverty."},{"time":576960,"text":"But for companies, it's providing\ninsights about your customers"},{"time":580000,"text":"and potential customers in India."},{"time":582760,"text":"It's a win all around."},{"time":585960,"text":"Now, for me, what I find\nexciting about data philanthropy --"},{"time":589760,"text":"donating data, donating decision\nscientists and donating technology --"},{"time":594120,"text":"it's what it means\nfor young professionals like me"},{"time":596520,"text":"who are choosing to work at companies."},{"time":598800,"text":"Studies show that\nthe next generation of the workforce"},{"time":601480,"text":"care about having their work\nmake a bigger impact."},{"time":604920,"text":"We want to make a difference,"},{"time":607400,"text":"and so through data philanthropy,"},{"time":609840,"text":"companies can actually help engage\nand retain their decision scientists."},{"time":613800,"text":"And that's a big deal for a profession\nthat's in high demand."}]},{"cues":[{"time":617840,"text":"Data philanthropy\nmakes good business sense,"},{"time":622200,"text":"and it also can help\nrevolutionize the humanitarian world."},{"time":627600,"text":"If we coordinated\nthe planning and logistics"},{"time":629720,"text":"across all of the major facets\nof a humanitarian operation,"},{"time":633120,"text":"we could feed, clothe and shelter\nhundreds of thousands more people,"},{"time":637440,"text":"and companies need to step up\nand play the role that I know they can"},{"time":641720,"text":"in bringing about this revolution."}]},{"cues":[{"time":644720,"text":"You've probably heard of the saying\n\"food for thought.\""},{"time":647680,"text":"Well, this is literally thought for food."},{"time":651560,"text":"It finally is the right idea\nat the right time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":655720,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":656960,"text":"Très magnifique."}]},{"cues":[{"time":658560,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":659800,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}